The teenager's body was discovered on Sunday. CAPE TOWN - The youth accused of the rape and murder of 14-year-old Ocean View girl is expected to apply for bail in the Simon's Town magistrates court on Wednesday.Cameron Britz' body was discovered on Sunday.Britz 19-year-old cousin made his first appearance in the Simons Town magistrates court on Wednesday.It is understood her cousin lured her away from a gathering under false pretenses.He s applied for Legal Aid, and it s expected that his counsel will have to provide evidence of exceptional circumstances in order for bail to be granted.(Edited by Shimoney Regter)